<para style="q1">

<verse number="8" style="v" />Oh that people would praise Yahweh for his covenant faithfulness</para>

<para style="q1">and for the amazing things he has done for humanity!</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="9" style="v" />For he satisfies the longings of those who are thirsty,</para>

<para style="q1">and the desires of those who are hungry he fills up with good things.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="10" style="v" />Some sat in darkness and in gloom,</para>

<para style="q1">prisoners in affliction and chains.</para>
